On April 13, 2001, we remanded this case to the trial court for that court to determine whether the arbitration clause contained in the \u8220\'3facknowledgment and agreement\u8221\'3f signed by the plaintiffs and by a representative of Cavalier Manufacturing, Inc. (\u8220\'3fCavalier\u8221\'3f), is valid, although the clause prohibits the arbitrator from awarding punitive damages. See 
